Package: measure
Title: A Recipes-Style Interface to Tidymodels for Analytical Measurements
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("James", "Wade", , "github@jameshwade.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9740-1905")),
    person("Max", "Kuhn", , "max@posit.co", role = "ctb",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2402-136X"))
    )
Description: Provides preprocessing steps for analytical measurement data
    such as spectroscopy and chromatography within the 'tidymodels' framework.
    Extends 'recipes' with steps for common spectral preprocessing techniques.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://jameshwade.github.io/measure/, https://github.com/JamesHWade/measure
